			 (2019), (2020), (2021), (2022),
			 (2023), (2024), (2025), (2026),
			 (2027), (2028), (2029), (2030), (2032),
			 (2033), (2033)$$,
	'Check bulk load outlines of related table after buildings comparison function has run'
